                </div>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="keynote-modal-profile">
                    <img src="/images/keynote/suresh_nair.png" alt="Dr. Suresh Nair" loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async" width="1600" height="907">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Ignite: Sparking the Entrepreneur Within</h3>
                        <p>Startups and innovations have become buzzwords among youngsters over the last few years. Many millennials dream of building a startup of their own, and many organisations have been built to support such innovations through incubation.</p>
                        <p>There are a few success stories, but not many innovative products seem to have emerged in the recent past. This talk will examine the current state of affairs, the gaps that need to be bridged, and the importance of focusing on quality proposals over quantity. The session will showcase personal case studies, with special emphasis on the hardware product development life cycle.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade keynote-details-modal" id="homeKeynoteSateeshModal" tabindex="-1"
    aria-labelledby="homeKeynoteSateeshTitle" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <div>
                    <span class="keynote-track">Cybersecurity Keynote</span>
                    <h2 class="modal-title" id="homeKeynoteSateeshTitle">Dr. Peddoju Sateesh Kumar</h2>
                    <p>Professor, IIT Roorkee</p>
                </div>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="keynote-modal-profile">
                    <img src="/images/keynote/sateesh_kumar.png" alt="Dr. Peddoju Sateesh Kumar" loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async" width="412" height="412">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Beyond Signatures: Detecting Obfuscated and Zero-Day Malware</h3>
                        <p>Security breaches continue to pose significant threats to individuals, organizations, and critical infrastructure, and malware remains the primary weapon in modern cyberattacks. Adversaries increasingly leverage sophisticated tools and AI-assisted techniques to craft malicious payloads that evade existing defenses with fewer resources than ever before.</p>
                        <p>While AI and ML models have become integral to modern malware detection systems because they can identify complex patterns and detect previously unseen malware, they remain vulnerable to adversarial manipulation. This talk presents novel detection models that go beyond conventional malware detection to specifically target advanced obfuscation techniques, including code injection, metamorphism, packing, and zero-day malware.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

